OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA breezy
OL,6,Fnight with most areas remaining dry
OL,7,Fwith clear spells likely across the
OL,8,Fregion. Southern areas will see risk
OL,9,Fof blustery showers, especially near
OL,10,Fcoasts. Chilly inland by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSome sunshine for Sunday but
OL,13,Fincreasingly showery with some
OL,14,Fbecoming heavy by afternoon brining a
OL,15,Frisk of thunder. A windy day with
OL,16,Ftemperatures mostly near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
