OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FSunshine and showers for Monday, with
OL,7,Fheavy downpours again. Drier by
OL,8,Fevening. Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,9,Fcloudier with increasing chance of
OL,10,Fshowery rain. Breezy, but milder with
OL,11,Fslightly above average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
